        <h2 class="section-title">Your Cosmetic Dermatology Journey</h2>
        <div class="process-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h3>Free Consultation</h3>
            <p>Comprehensive skin analysis with our dermatologist to understand your concerns and aesthetic goals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h3>Custom Treatment Plan</h3>
            <p>Personalised plan combining the right procedures, timeline, and realistic expectations for your goals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
